@Node "MUI" "MUI"


@{b}MUI@{ub}
@{u}                                                                 @{uu}


  This application uses:

  @{fg shine}MUI@{fg text} - @{fg shine}MagicUserInterface@{fg text}
  Copyright 1992-2002 by @{fg shine}Stefan Stuntz@{fg text}

  @{fg shine}MUI@{fg text} is a system to generate and maintain graphical user
  interfaces. With the aid of a preferences program, the user of
  an application has the ability to customize the outfit
  according to his personal taste

  @{fg shine}MUI@{fg text} is distributed as shareware. To obtain a complete package
  containing a lot of examples and more information about
  registration please look for a file called muiXXusr.lha (XX
  means the latest version number) on your local bulletin boards
  or on public domain disks.

