       opened

     o A window is not created if its Contents is not defined.

     o Any graphical object must be added to a window to be
     visible

  See @{"Application" LINK "ApplicationClass"}.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Activate@{fg text}
  B ISGN

  @{fg shine}ActiveObject@{fg text}
  S SG

  @{fg shine}AltHeight@{fg text}
  N IG
  Special values:
   MinMax(p) 0-p
   Visible(p) -100-p
   Screen(p) -200-p
   Scaled(p) -1000

  AltLeftEdge N IG
  Special values:
   Centered -1
   Moused -2
   NoChange -1000

  @{fg shine}AltTopEdge@{fg text}
  N IG
  Special values:
  Centered -1
  Moused -2
  Delta(p) -3-p
  NoChange -1000

  @{fg shine}AltWidth@{fg text}
  N IG
  Special values:
  MinMax(p) 0-p
  Visible(p) -100-p
  Screen(p) -200-p
  Scaled(p) -1000

  @{fg shine}AppMessage@{fg text}
  B GN

  @{fg shine}AppWindow@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}BackDrop@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}BorderLess@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}CloseGadget@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}CloseRequest@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}Contents@{fg text}
  S I IND

  @{fg shine}DefaultObject@{fg text}
  S S

  @{fg shine}DepthGadget@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}DragBar@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}Height@{fg text}
  N IG
  Special values:
      o MinMax(p) 0-p
      o Visible(p) -100-p
      o Screen(p) -200-p
      o Scaled(p) -1000
      o Default -1001

  @{fg shine}ID@{fg text}
  M I

  @{fg shine}InputEvent@{fg text}
  S N
  Used in notifications like
      call Notify("mwin","InputEvent","ramiga b","app","Return","call GoURL('BACK')")
  to make a method be invoked on an object when a keys
  combination is played.



  @{fg shine}LeftEdge@{fg text}
  N IG
  Special values:
      o Centered -1
      o Moused -2

  @{fg shine}MenuStrip@{fg text}
  S I

  @{fg shine}NoMenus@{fg text}
  B IS

  @{fg shine}Open@{fg text}
